Printing RYX Function

print.ryx.Rd

Prints RXY function in a neat clean way

Usage

# S3 method for class 'ryx'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

the results from "rxy" function

Value

A formatted print of the results of the "rxy" function

Examples

library(MASS)
data(Boston)
print(ryx(Boston, y="medv"))
